(277, 85, 'research_description', 'During the research phase I noticed that many of the choirs throughout the U.S.A. do not have a solid online presence and many of the sites look quite outdated and quite frankly put a bad taste in your mouth. I wanted to create something that looked just as good as the boys sound and could appeal to a kid wanting to have fun and make friends and parents that want a wonderful youth program for their young boy to grow and mature in.\r\n\r\n<h5>Some Competitors</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li><a href="http://www.sccchorus.org/">Southern California Children''s Chorus</a></li>\r\n <li><a href="http://www.noccc.com/">New Orange County Children''s Chorus</li>\r\n <li><a href="http://www.youngsingersoc.org/">Young Singers of Orange County</a></li>\r\n</ul>'),
