(1085, 295, 'typography_description', 'The typography for this design was really important for me. I wanted to create a typeface for the brand that fit this high performance nutritional snack. I wanted something that was sleek but strong. I went with creating a typeface that was bold in physique but curved all the edges off to keep the feeling of a smooth nutritional snack. '),
